  |   arcade version for the first time. It is possible to set two game     |
  |   modes: Normal race and Grand Prix race, which was only possible in    |
  |   the arcade board settings. Race 4 to 5 laps in Normal mode, and       |
  |   endurance play 20 laps in Grand Prix mode. In Grand Prix mode, tire   |
  |   changes timing in the pit is also an important strategy, as           |
  |   continuing to drive will wear the tires and affect handling.          |
